10:T579,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"TVSeries","name":"The King's Avatar","description":"Widely regarded as a trailblazer and top-tier professional player in the online multiplayer game \"Glory,\" Xiu Ye is dubbed the \"Battle God\" for his skills and contributions to the game over the years. However, when forced to retire from the team and to leave his gaming career behind, he finds work at a nearby internet café. There, when Glory launches its 10th server, he throws himself into the game once more using a new character named \"Lord Grim.\"\n\nXiu Ye's early achievements on the new server immediately catch the attention of many players, as well as the big guilds, leaving them to wonder about the identity of this exceptional player. However, while he possesses 10 years of experience and in-depth knowledge, starting afresh with neither sponsors nor a team in a game that has changed over the years presents numerous challenges. Along with talented new comrades, Xiu Ye once again dedicates himself to traversing the path to Glory's summit.","image":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx98861-MMwQxW1S8WkF.jpg","datePublished":"2017-04-07","numberOfEpisodes":12,"countryOfOrigin":"CN","inLanguage":"cn","genre":["Action","Drama"],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":7.5,"bestRating":10,"ratingCount":0}}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$10"}}],["$","$L11",null,{"initialDrama":{"id":"609a74d6-f53e-45ea-a670-4f9d33fd802d","tmdb_id":98861,"imdb_id":null,"content_type":"anime","title":"The King's Avatar","original_title":"全职高手","overview":"Widely regarded as a trailblazer and top-tier professional player in the online multiplayer game \"Glory,\" Xiu Ye is dubbed the \"Battle God\" for his skills and contributions to the game over the years. However, when forced to retire from the team and to leave his gaming career behind, he finds work at a nearby internet café. There, when Glory launches its 10th server, he throws himself into the game once more using a new character named \"Lord Grim.\"\n\nXiu Ye's early achievements on the new server immediately catch the attention of many players, as well as the big guilds, leaving them to wonder about the identity of this exceptional player. However, while he possesses 10 years of experience and in-depth knowledge, starting afresh with neither sponsors nor a team in a game that has changed over the years presents numerous challenges. Along with talented new comrades, Xiu Ye once again dedicates himself to traversing the path to Glory's summit.","poster_path":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx98861-MMwQxW1S8WkF.jpg","backdrop_path":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/98861-vDeVlvjXHh0g.jpg","release_date":null,"first_air_date":"2017-04-07","status":"published","original_language":"cn","origin_country":["CN"],"genres":[{"id":1,"name":"Action"},{"id":2,"name":"Drama"}],"popularity":85671,"vote_average":7.5,"vote_count":null,"runtime":24,"number_of_seasons":null,"number_of_episodes":12,"created_at":"2026-05-02T08:50:50.033939+00:00","updated_at":"2026-05-02T08:50:49.992+00:00","tagline":null,"homepage":null,"budget":null,"revenue":null,"production_companies":[{"name":"G.CMay Animation & Film"},{"name":"K.PICTURES"}],"production_countries":null,"spoken_languages":null,"networks":[],"last_air_date":"2017-06-16","in_production":false,"tmdb_status":"Ended","content_rating":null,"keywords":[{"id":1,"name":"E-Sports"},{"id":2,"name":"Video Games"},{"id":3,"name":"Virtual World"},{"id":4,"name":"Male Protagonist"},{"id":5,"name":"Primarily Adult Cast"},{"id":6,"name":"Ensemble Cast"}],"alternative_titles":null,"videos":[],"watch_providers":null,"wikidata_id":null,"tvdb_id":null,"wikipedia_url":null,"overview_source":"tmdb","import_batch_id":null,"import_batch_name":null,"imported_at":"2026-05-02T08:50:50.033939+00